notify the Elders to come save us.

335
00:30:52,350 --> 00:30:56,020
That won't do. Him being here alone is sufficient.

336
00:30:56,020 --> 00:30:57,540
I have to go with all of you.

337
00:30:57,540 --> 00:30:59,510
How can you be this kind of person--

338
00:31:05,190 --> 00:31:07,460
I know that all of you don’t welcome me.

339
00:31:07,460 --> 00:31:12,510
If once I’m done explaining the main matter and all
of you still won’t help, I won’t nag you anymore.

340
00:31:12,510 --> 00:31:15,960
Say it. What's the matter?

341
00:31:31,660 --> 00:31:34,730
I really didn’t expect there would come a day
when I'd be a partner with her.

342
00:31:34,730 --> 00:31:38,210
Xun'er, in order to who controlled the Emperor,

343
00:31:38,210 --> 00:31:42,030
and to find Elder Mi Tengshan,
we have no choice but to do it this way.

344
00:31:42,030 --> 00:31:46,220
Then can’t we just go by ourselves to investigate?
Why must we bring her along?

345
00:31:47,610 --> 00:31:49,780
It's already alerted them yesterday,

346
00:31:49,780 --> 00:31:52,610
so today we must quickly find out the truth.

347
00:31:52,610 --> 00:31:54,840
I hope you can think for the Chu Yun Empire

348
00:31:54,840 --> 00:31:57,420
and temporarily set aside any grudges between us.

349
00:31:58,900 --> 00:32:00,400
What do you mean?

350
00:32:00,400 --> 00:32:03,680
You’re very kind and righteous.
I’m selfish.

351
00:32:08,830 --> 00:32:11,800
- Brother Xiao Yan, are you all right?
- I'm fine.

352
00:32:11,800 --> 00:32:14,350
I was injured internally yesterday.
I’m still not well.

353
00:32:15,700 --> 00:32:19,480
I’m sandwiched in between you all,
just like an especially bright burning candle.

354
00:32:19,480 --> 00:32:21,620
I don’t care what kind of
animosity there is among all of you.

355
00:32:21,620 --> 00:32:23,360
I’m going ahead first.

356
00:32:26,780 --> 00:32:28,890
I’m fine. I’m fine.
Let’s hurry and keep going.

357
00:32:28,890 --> 00:32:30,730
Go...

358
00:32:39,930 --> 00:32:43,120
Early every morning is when the complete
Imperial Palace Minister group gathers here.

359
00:32:43,120 --> 00:32:47,410
We'll enter with them. Wait until dawn
and watch for my signal to take action.

360
00:32:47,410 --> 00:32:50,630
Disrupting the morning Imperial Court is
a huge crime. You’re a Prime Minister.

361
00:32:50,630 --> 00:32:52,690
Of course, I'll take responsibility.

362
00:32:52,690 --> 00:32:55,470
Both of you have been here before?

363
00:33:01,730 --> 00:33:03,580
Brother Xiao Yan.

364
00:33:06,710 --> 00:33:08,060
Yes.

365
00:33:08,060 --> 00:33:09,350
When?

366
00:33:09,350 --> 00:33:10,990
Last night.

367
00:33:10,990 --> 00:33:13,390
Weren’t you alone?

368
00:33:13,390 --> 00:33:16,090
