So I didn’t say it.

369
00:33:16,090 --> 00:33:17,790
Really?

370
00:33:23,870 --> 00:33:28,020
Acting. Keep on acting. Throw up again.

371
00:33:28,020 --> 00:33:31,550
Continuously throwing up will harm the body.
You’re unwilling to make me do that, right?

372
00:33:31,550 --> 00:33:33,100
I'm willing.

373
00:33:46,780 --> 00:33:50,280
I only did it in order to save Elder Mi Tengshan.

374
00:33:52,560 --> 00:33:56,040
Fine. Then I forgive you.

375
00:35:33,130 --> 00:35:34,780
Your Majesty?

376
00:35:36,170 --> 00:35:37,800
Xiao Yan.

377
00:35:39,970 --> 00:35:41,530
Your Majesty.

378
00:35:47,720 --> 00:35:49,340
Your Majesty...

379
00:35:55,200 --> 00:35:57,560
You are finally here.

380
00:35:59,500 --> 00:36:04,410
You are a bit later than I expected.

381
00:36:14,600 --> 00:36:19,750
Xiao Family, Nalan Clan, Gu Tribe,

382
00:36:19,750 --> 00:36:22,250
all of you are here.

383
00:36:22,250 --> 00:36:25,620
Good. Very good.

384
00:36:26,320 --> 00:36:29,470
After eliminating meddlesome people like you,

385
00:36:29,470 --> 00:36:32,300
the whole Chu Yun Empire

386
00:36:32,300 --> 00:36:35,820
will now come under our Soul Hall.

387
00:36:37,400 --> 00:36:39,440
You are not the Emperor.

388
00:36:40,210 --> 00:36:42,260
Who are you really?

389
00:36:42,260 --> 00:36:45,340
It was you
